@startuml command-recorder-states
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam stateBorderColor #888

title CommandRecorder State Flow

[*] --> Idle : Create

Idle --> Recording : Begin()
Idle --> [*] : Destroy

Recording --> InRenderPass : BeginRenderPass()
Recording --> Finished : Finish()

InRenderPass --> Recording : EndRenderPass()
InRenderPass --> InRenderPass : Draw Commands
InRenderPass --> Error : Invalid Operation

state Recording {
    [*] --> Ready
    Ready : Can begin render pass
    Ready : Can update resources
    Ready : Can copy textures
    Ready --> Ready : Resource Operations
}

state InRenderPass {
    [*] --> Drawing
    Drawing : SetPipeline()
    Drawing : SetBindGroup()
    Drawing : SetVertexBuffer()
    Drawing : Draw()
    Drawing : DrawIndexed()
    Drawing --> Drawing : Draw Commands
    
    note right of Drawing
        **Valid Operations:**
        - All draw commands
        - Pipeline state changes
        - Resource bindings
        
        **Invalid Operations:**
        - BeginRenderPass (nested)
        - Resource creation
        - Buffer updates
    end note
}

Finished --> Idle : Reset()\n(Reuse)
Finished --> Submitted : Submit()

Submitted --> [*] : Frame Complete

Error --> [*] : Exception

note left of Error
    **Common Errors:**
    - BeginRenderPass without End
    - Draw without pipeline
    - Finish with active pass
    - Use after Finish
end note

note bottom of Recording
    **RenderPass Rules:**
    - Must explicitly EndRenderPass
    - No auto-close on BeginRenderPass
    - No auto-close on Finish (error)
end note

@enduml